Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有卖哦  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶用这个就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就先用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…纯  拿个篮子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…还有牙签和什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我们收据
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,署名就写「樱丘女子高等学校2年1班」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有附文…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就写「学园祭模拟店茶费」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶也一起买了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个等不够了再买也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么会变得这么手忙脚乱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天就是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且手忙脚乱才感觉有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:33.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天轻音部的演唱会没有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:35.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回教室去吧
